text: Mohamed Ould Brahim (born 3 January 1968), is a Mauritanian athlete. Brahim competed in the 200 metres at the 1996 Summer Olympics, he finished 8th in his heat so didn't qualify for the next round. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic athletes of Mauritania Category:Mauritanian male sprinters Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1996 Summer Olympics
